      <minor />
      <comment>[[WP:CHECKWIKI]] error fixes + [[WP:GENFIXES|general fixes]] using [[Project:AWB|AWB]] (7708)</comment>
      <text xml:space="preserve">{{redirect|Afonso I|the African ruler|Afonso I of Kongo}}
{{Infobox royalty
| type            =monarch
| name            =Afonso I
| title           =King of the Portuguese
| image           =AfonsoI-P.jpg
|succession=[[List of Portuguese monarchs|Count, then King of Portuguese]]
| reign     =1 November 1112–6 December 1185&lt;br&gt;({{age in years and days|1112|11|1|1185|12|6}})
| coronation    ={{death date and age|1139|7|26|1109|6|25|df=y}}
| predecessor     =[[Theresa, Countess of Portugal|Queen Teresa, Countess of Portugal]] &lt;small&gt;(''de jure'' and ''de facto'')&lt;/small&gt;
| successor       =[[Sancho I of Portugal|Sancho I]]
| spouse          =[[Maud of Savoy]]
| issue           =[[Urraca of Portugal|Urraca, Queen of León]]&lt;br&gt;[[Sancho I of Portugal|Sancho I]]&lt;br&gt;[[Infanta Teresa, Countess of Flanders]]
| issue-link      = #Descendants
| issue-pipe      = among others ...
| house     =[[House of Capet|Capetian]] [[House of Burgundy]]
