| issue           =[[Infanta Branca of Portugal|Infanta Branca]]&lt;br/&gt; [[Denis of Portugal|Denis]]&lt;br/&gt; [[Infante Afonso, Lord of Portalegre]]&lt;br/&gt; [[Infanta Sancha of Portugal|Infanta Sancha]]&lt;br/&gt; [[Infanta Maria of Portugal (nun)|Infanta Maria]]
