==Marriage and descendants==
Afonso married [[Beatrice of Castile (1293–1359)|Beatrice of Castile]] (1293–1359) in 1309, daughter of [[Sancho IV of Castile|Sancho IV]], [[King of Castile]], and [[María de Molina]] and had four sons and three daughters.

